<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>حَدَّثَنَا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١٦٧٤٣ - ابْنُ عُيَيْنَةَ، عَنْ عَبْدِ الْكَرِيمِ، عَنْ سَعِيدِ بْنِ الْمُسَيِّبِ،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«لَا يَتَزَوَّجُ حَتَّى تَنْقَضِيَ عِدَّةُ الَّتِي طَلَّقَ»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>